.TH ASENSE 1 "20 July 2026" "ASense 0.2.2" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
asense \- Acer laptop control center
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B asense
.RI [ option ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ASense
is a graphical Linux control center for supported Acer Predator and Nitro
laptops.  Available controls are discovered independently from Linux
platform-profile, hwmon, Acer WMI and supported HID interfaces.
.PP
Running the command without an option opens or focuses the graphical control
panel.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B probe, --probe
Print a local, read-only JSON capability report to standard output.  The
report omits serial numbers, UUIDs, account names and network identifiers.
.TP
.B --toggle
Open ASense when it is closed, or close the existing ASense window.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/asense/desktop-user
Desktop account authorized to use the private ASense control socket.
.TP
.I /run/asense-control.sock
Private socket used to communicate with the privileged ASense daemon.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR asense-configure-user (8)
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at https://github.com/fladirm/asense/issues.
